data.description: HONEY STOP THE CAR, THIS IS THE ONE! NO HOA! Welcome to your Dream Home at 14925 Mockingbird Ln E, Clearwater, FL 33760, where modern elegance meets Florida charm! This meticulously maintained property offers an array of desirable features that make it a must-see for anyone seeking a comfortable and stylish living space. Plenty of parking is available for your toys with the widened driveway and side yard parking with a crushed limestone base that is perfect for those with boats, RVs, or multiple vehicles. Step into the heart of the home. Great Room Floor Plan with Shiplap Walls and Dining area- Great for Entertaining. Newly remodeled Kitchen boasting Stainless-Steel Appliances, Gas Range, Decorative Subway Tile Backsplash & Ceramic Tile Flooring. Large Master Bedroom with plenty of Closet space and French Door to Patio. Second Bedroom shares the adjacent Updated Bath with Ceramic Tile, Shiplap Walls, Subway Tile Tub/Shower Combo, New Vanity and Updated Fixtures. New Wood-like Flooring & Ceramic Tile throughout! Enjoy the convenience of a new garage door, adding both security and style to your property. Embrace the Florida lifestyle in your own backyard. Large in-ground pool with a new sand filter! Relax or entertain guests on the covered back porch, providing shade and comfort! Freshly Painted Exterior. Classic white picket fence graces the front yard, adding a picturesque and inviting touch to your home. This Clearwater gem offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and Florida living. Schedule a viewing today and experience the magic of this exceptional property firsthand. Your dream home awaits! HVAC/AC 2020. Great Location, Close to Restaurants, Shopping, Beaches and Airports.
